PaymentController, PaymentService and models (IPaymentGateway - interface) and other implementations of interfaces corresponding to different gateways.
Adapter design pattern is followed here


webhook:
    localtunnel for exposing endpoint of our service which will be called by razorpay
    Localtunnel allows you to easily share a web service on your local development machine without messing with DNS and firewall settings.

    npm install -g localtunnel
    lt --port 8000  (the port on which payment service is running)

    in stripe dashboard, webhook is configured.

